<p>This week we answer all your questions and queries about which router you should buy and how to go about deciding this for yourself. Standalone vs. mesh, eero vs. Orbi, 2&#215;2 vs 4&#215;4, we cover it all. After listening to this episode you&#039;ll have both the information and even some deals to be able to make your choice and know you&#039;ve got the right Wi-Fi for your home.Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
